# CloudMail source-of-truth baseline .gitignore
# Baseline captures authoritative SOURCE (code, config, migrations, docs, reports).
# Derived/binary/large artifacts and ALL secret material are excluded by design.
# Rationale: docs/ADR-REPOSITORY-AUTHORITY-RESTORATION.md

# --- Secrets & signing material (NEVER commit) ---
profile/
*.p12
*.mobileprovision
*.certSigningRequest
*.pem
*.key
id_rsa*
.env
.env.*
*.env
**/.dev.vars
*service-account*.json
*credentials*.json
signing-work/

# --- Derived / build artifacts (reproducible, large) ---
artifacts/
build/
platform/build/
archive/
evidence/
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
**/DerivedData*/
**/Build/
**/Logs/
dist/
**/dist/
.wrangler/
**/.wrangler/
*.xcarchive/
*.xcresult/
*.dSYM/
xcuserdata/
**/xcuserdata/

# --- Packaged apps / archives ---
*.ipa
*.zip
*.zip.*
*.tar
*.tar.gz

# --- Binary / media (evidence artifacts, not source) ---
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.heic
*.HEIC
*.gif
*.mp4
*.mov
nexora logo/

# --- OS cruft ---
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
